=James Morris Hargett=
* research on song travel literature [[范成大]]
==Publications==
===PhD Dissertation===
* The poetry of Chen Yu-yi (1090-1139). Indiana University, 1982
===Monographs===
* On the Road in Twelfth Century China: The Travel Diaries of Fan Chengda, Stuttgart: Franz Steiner Verlag, 1989
* Stairway to Heaven: A Journey to the Summit of Mount Emei, Albany: New York: SUNY Press, 2006
* Riding the River Home: A Complete and Annotated Translation of Fan Chengda's (1126-1193) Diary of a Boat Trip to Wu (Wuchuan lu), The Chinese University Press, Hong Kong, 2008
