* "Playing Second Fiddle: The Luan-Bird in Early and Medieval Chinese Literature." T'oung Pao, Volume 75, No. 4/5, 1989, pp. 235-262
* "Song Dynasty Local Gazetteers and Their Place in The History of Difangzhi Writing." Harvard Journal of Asiatic Studies, Volume 56, No. 2, 1996, pp. 405-442
